videos.description: Gary Trent Jr sinks a 3-pointer off the assist from Marvin Bagley III.
videos.headline: Duke's Bagley finds Trent in corner for 3

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III cleans up the Gary Trent Jr. miss with a putback slam.
videos.headline: Duke's Bagley gets putback dunk

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III drills two 3-pointers as part of 71 first-half points for the Blue Devils.
videos.headline: Duke's Bagley knocks down consecutive 3s

videos.description: Grayson Allen takes the pass from Gary Trent Jr. and finishes with a dunk.
videos.headline: Duke's Allen puts down slam
